{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make GCSE Science an optional subject",
        "additional_details": "If not made optional, students who fail GCSE science should be forced to resit it, bringing it in line with the requirements for GCSE English and Maths which are both also mandatory subjects. ",
        "background": "I think that GCSE Science should be made an optional subject. I think that students should not be forced to take science as a subject. ",
